[Server 17:24:05.27 INFO]: Kinger: I don t know.
[Server 17:24:06.86 INFO]: Ragatha: Wh-- What do you mean?
[Server 17:24:08.66 INFO]: Kinger: But everything s gonna be okay. Do you... remember your name?.
[Server 17:24:11.23 INFO]: Ragatha: I m -- I -- I m...
[Server 17:24:15.70 WARN]: [Mappy] Warning: Ragatha is too vulnerable to Abstraction. Proceed with caution!
> PRESENT DAY...[Server 17:24:23.19 INFO]: Pomni: Ragatha?
[Server 17:24:23.95 INFO]: Ragatha: Huh?
[Server 17:24:25.47 INFO]: Pomni: You doing okay?
[Server 17:24:26.72 INFO]: Ragatha: That s a good question.
[Server 17:24:31.05 INFO]: Jax: Welp, really hate to say it, guys, but I told--
[Server 17:24:40.55 INFO]: Zooble: Dont you even! Do not even [boing] BEGIN to say that sentence like you didn t try to keep us all trapped here forever.
[Server 17:24:47.44 INFO]: Jax: Anything could have happened when you pressed those buttons. It doesn t matter.
[Server 17:24:50.21 INFO]: Zooble: It seemed to matter back when you did it. What if you DID ruin our one chance at leaving?
[Server 17:24:55.17 INFO]: Jax: And what if Abel was secretly evil? What if we all got stranded in the void? What if, what if, what if.
[Server 17:25:02.25 INFO]: Jax: It wasn t real... So it doesn t matter. Never did.
[Server 17:25:04.13 INFO]: Zooble: How can you say that like you didn t try to [boing] us all over?
[Server 17:25:11.16 INFO]: Gangle: He s right, though.
[Server 17:25:15.46 INFO]: Zooble: What? Gangle.
[Server 17:25:16.63 INFO]: Gangle: It doesn t matter what could have happened. We could argue about it and hurt each other all day long, but that s not gonna help anybody. I think... what we need to do now... is to just be there for each other.
[Server 17:25:34.80 INFO]: Pomni: She s right. We ve all done bad things. But we re also all we ve got. (inhales deeply, then sighs) I think... we need to abandon the idea of leaving.
[Server 17:25:52.83 INFO]: Zooble: What -- What are you --
[Server 17:25:54.05 INFO]: Pomni: We got our hopes up, and we were let down. I don t know what exactly happened with Kaufmo... But we can t let that despair consume us. We should focus on what we have.
[Server 17:26:05.68 INFO]: Pomni: Like you said... constantly chasing an unobtainable goal will drive us crazy. Maybe what we have to do now is to just... live.
[Server 17:26:24.90 INFO]: Zooble: Oh, man. I had dreams... and -- and goals. I wanted to be able to leave my mark somewhere in the world. How am I supposed to just abandon that?
[Server 17:26:42.11 INFO]: Gangle: You ve made a mark in my life.
[Server 17:26:47.67 INFO]: (Camera cuts to a distressed Zooble.)
[Server 17:26:49.57 INFO]: Zooble: Oh, man. I had dreams... and -- and goals. I wanted to be able to leave my mark somewhere in the world. How am I supposed to just abandon that?
[Server 17:26:52.27 INFO]: Gangle: You ve made a mark in my life.
[Server 17:26:53.35 INFO]: (Zooble looks at her solemnly.)
[Server 17:26:54.87 INFO]: Zooble: (sighs) I know. You re probably right. But...
[Server 17:26:57.64 INFO]: (Tears form in Zooble s eyes.)
[Server 17:26:58.63 INFO]: Zooble: It just... really, really sucks.
[Server 17:26:59.65 INFO]: (Gangle lifts her arm onto Zooble s back, then Zooble gives her a big hug, still in tears. Gangle hugs back.)
[Server 17:27:02.56 INFO]: Ragatha: We re all in this together.
[Server 17:27:04.67 INFO]: Pomni: And we ll always be in this together. No matter what.
[Server 17:27:08.03 INFO]: (Jax leaves the couch and walks away)
[Server 17:27:16.72 INFO]: Zooble: Hey. That includes you, too.
[Server 17:27:20.60 INFO]: Jax: Huh?
[Server 17:27:21.75 INFO]: Zooble: (sighs) Listen, we re not gonna have you wandering off alone somewhere and abstracting, or something. You re a pain in the [boing], but... you re still one of us.
[Server 17:27:30.81 INFO]: Jax: You -- (stammers, looking in his right hand shaking before going back at couch and lies back) Heh. You think I m capable of abstracting? You guys worry too much.
[Server 17:27:49.94 INFO]: (Jax looks at Pomni before making a smile on her face, he looks away, which makes Pomni visibly sad.)
[Server 17:27:52.14 INFO]: Zooble: (sighs) We need a vacation.
